Author: provocome
Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: https://i.imgur.com/VLSVl9N.png  In 2014 a charity-driven challenge emerged — ALS Ice Bucket Challenge. It challenged people either to donate $100 to the ALS, or to otherwise douse themselves with a bucket of ice-cold water while filming themselves as well as making a smaller donation and tagging three others with the same provocation. In few months this challenge raised $220 million dollars and gathered over 1 billion views on YouTube. As the dare propagated, it tagged various celebrities and people with large numbers of social followers, causing the challenge to grow in a viral manner. People became interested in these challenges and until 2018 we already had 16 viral challenges that raised well over $1 billion dollars and gathered over 300 billion views. PROVOCO is a platform that will revolutionise the whole social challenge industry and will help you earn unreal amounts of money while doing these or creating different challenges.  Full article on medium

Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: https://i.imgur.com/EqQKi1Z.jpg  The value and power of social networks has become globally important, and it is growing every year. Social networking sites dominate not just the Internet, but the economy as a whole. Almost every person all around the world interacts with social networks directly or indirectly every day.  Social networks have become a part of our daily lives for activities, such as personal relationships, work, entertainment, and studies.  Social media — is a usually a web application that people use to build social networks or social relations with other people who share similar personal or career interests, activities, backgrounds or real-life connections.. Social networks are now so well established, that there is a core ‘top 5’ social networks that don’t change much from year-to-year.  Most popular social media sites vary a lot by level of usage in different countries and demographics.  Provoco is here to change that!  Full Aricle on Medium

Author: provocome
Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: https://i.imgur.com/MgRGkuv.jpg  Why decenralization is important? After the Facebook–Cambridge Analytica data scandal, centralized social media platforms have been in the hot seat with intensifying public scrutiny on how personal data is being managed and used. This not only paved way for the GDPR privacy regulations that came into force recently but also gave rise to what is called blockchain social networking.  The personal data of up to 87 million users, mostly in the U.S., was obtained by an analytics firm that, among its other work, helped elect President Donald Trump. In response to that revelation, lawmakers and regulators in the U.S. and U.K. increased their scrutiny of the social media giant, and at least some Facebook users canceled their accounts. The uproar has only added to the pressure on Facebook and Chief Executive Mark Zuckerberg over how the company was used during the 2016 presidential campaign to spread Russian propaganda and phony headlines.  Full article on Medium

Author: elitecstrike
Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: Provoco (VOCO) token use cases  There are more than 1600 cryptocurrency projects in the market. In fact, this is a very huge supply, because a lot of tokens are worthless and have a very narrow use cases. While we have such a huge supply it’s very hard for businesses to keep demand on their token because a lot of investors seeks only for value growth.  Utility tokens may grow in price, if the demand for service or product increases. If the price goes up too much, the demand, that is driven by use case, will decline, and in reaction to that price will also decrease. At the same time if price falls, demand increases — and soon price will stabilize. The main aim is growing, or at least stable, demand, which can be assured by constant development of the token-related project. https://medium.com/@Provocome/provoco-voco-token-use-cases-21d17d2f7c7c

Author: provocome
Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*YSI-DQ3Ib_SFydD0mH_t4w.jpeg  In 2017 our team came up with an idea to create a brand new social network that would revolutionise the whole industry — Provoco, a social challenge network empowered by the blockchain. In a year we gained a lot of true followers, investors and fans who believed in an idea that challenges could change the whole social base we have right now. Because we believe so much in our platform we decided to take a huge gamble and made a decision only few ICO’s have ever done — we did a huge rebrand, both in style and in our idea. We listen to our loyal community and now we are new Provoco — a challenge network were people can create or accept challenges and earn for doing so.  New website  https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*2y2KbfH9Og1Opc9AP6F1RA.jpeg  We have heard a lot of different opinions from our community about the style we are going for. Provoco is a social network were you accept challenges, it needs to be more adventurous and free, so we decided to make it like that — an all new design made from ground up, a design that represents our idea and represents our whole fanbase. On our new website you can see a design that is made for a variety of people — it is made for everyone, no matter the age or culture. A bit of POP, comics and pixel art represent our idea perfectly — a mash between different styles create a new way of interacting and experiencing our platform.  You can check our new website right here — http://www.provoco.me  Wallet Updates  Our new explainer video  Tokenomy — a huge change  Rebranded Whitepaper and Onepage  And much more, please read on our Medium post:  https://medium.com/@Provocome/provoco-rebrand-challenge-yourself-4f416e97df75

Author: provocome
Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: Social challenges are becoming more and more mainstream - every month we can see tons of different examples of these internet phenomenons going viral, ranging from harmless to horrifying: silly ones (such as the Mannequin Challenge); helpful charity ones (like the ALS Ice Bucket Challenge) and slightly riskier ones (such as the Make Your Own Slime or The Knife Game). These provocations have changed the world forever - for example, ALS Ice Bucket Challenge raised well over $220 million dollars and in 2014 it reached just over 1 billion views on YouTube. Today we will cover some of the biggest and most entertaining challenges that have happened in the past couple of years and how they became an anomaly that united all of the internet.  Full article on Steemit   https://i.imgur.com/HAKI7p2.jpg

Author: wiserico
Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: Provoco  has been added to  WISERICO tracker    Vote for the Provoco on WISERICO and follow Provoco on the  media platforms:  Telegram Twitter Facebook Medium   Provoco is the world’s first Social Challenge Network powered by the Ethereum Blockchain. On the Provovo social network, every member can create and take challenges. High quality, entertaining and interesting challenge related video content will be accessible for every portal visitor. Here we will integrate traditional social network features and the advantages of video platforms. The ability to search and review attractive content as well as opportunities for earning revenue will encourage members to become active within our ecosystem. VOCO token supply will be limited and governed by the VOCO Fund, which will release them in an official Initial Coin Offering (ICO) event. It will be distributed exclusively through PROVOCO platform, which also be the first commercial product for the token use. VOCO Fund will be responsible for the management and administration of collected fund distribution to the PROVOCO project and searching for and granting future projects who will wish to join the VOCO Ecosystem.   WISERICO on BITCOINTALK

Author: provocome
Title: [ANN][ICO]👅PROVOCO.ME - Challenge Network for Ethereum Blockchain
Body: Hello,  Let us present the first challenge with Provoco! - https://provoco.me/en/new/first-challenge-provocome/ - Dakar Rally, here we come  We are at the very top of the development of Provoco.me, and we are also started to create and take real challenges. The first challenge with the #provocome brand was chosen to be truly exclusive. Our logo will travel the entire Dakar Rally. Mindaugas Plukys will carry the logo as the symbol of his challenge. He is not a professional racer, but has set himself up a difficult and exciting challenge. Together with the world’s most famous racers he will go with s Nissan Navara which is specially prepared for sands and this race. Of course, his goal is not to win the race, but to overcome himself by driving the whole 9000 km-long world’s toughest racing track and reach the finish line.  Provoco.me team

Very soon we are announcing all ICO/crowd sale details. Stay tuned  Provoco.me
